# But DO ship the warehouse + summary + models so the Docker image deployed
# to Render boots with real data. These are small (warehouse ~13MB) and
# the alternative (ghcr.io or release artifacts) is more moving parts.
!data/warehouse.duckdb
!data/backtests/summary_latest.json
!data/models/**

